{"type": "article", "id": 30920, "title": "梅西百货计划关店 100 家，以及，推荐 Carhartt WIP 东京街拍 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-12T02:14:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 253, "name": "LINE"}, {"id": 31426, "name": "Carhartt WIP"}, {"id": 31427, "name": "Fred Segal"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 1995, "name": "3.1 Phillip Lim"}, {"id": 9942, "name": "Elizabeth Arden"}, {"id": 17963, "name": "Madewell"}, {"id": 31428, "name": "Zalando"}, {"id": 31429, "name": "Dillard’s"}, {"id": 16286, "name": "Kendall Jenner"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160812094520UeVAI4ZDnht1sXLo.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/elizabeth-arden-posts-loss-fiscal-10504716/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elizabeth Arden 业绩下滑</a>&nbsp;</b>| Elizabeth Arden 这个季度的财报显示，该公司净亏损  2370 万美元，第一季度销售额 1.927 亿美元，比去年同期上涨了 9.8%。Elizabeth Arden 预计在 2016 年底完成与 Revlon 的并购。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/zalando-q2-net-profit-berlin-10504947/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>德国电商巨头 Zalando 第二季度业绩大涨 </b></a>| 得益于第二季度用户数量上涨了 15%，Zalando 第二季度净收入上涨了 121%，至 0.575 亿美元。Zalando 的董事会成员 Rubin Ritter 表示，该网站较低的产品价格，是吸引用户的主要原因。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/financial/dillards-posted-q2-profit-decline-retail-10505549/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国 Dillard’s 百货公司利润暴跌</b></a> | Dillard’s 第二季度利润暴跌 59.5%，尽管女装、男装和珠宝部分表现良好，由于家居部分差强人意， Dillard’s 第二季度净收入跌了 35.8%，至 8950 万美元。&nbsp;</p><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/department-stores/amid-declining-sales-macys-shutter-100-stores-10505001/\" rel=\"nofollow\">梅西百货计划关店 100 家</a> </b>| 第二季度，梅西的销售额下降了 3.9%，至 58.7 亿美元，去年同期则为 61 亿美元。由于业绩低迷，梅西百货计划要关 100 家店。关闭这些店将直接导致约 10 亿美元的损失，但是梅西认为，它此后会将更多的精力放在销量最好的前 150 家店上，同时也会积极寻求新的供应商、开发独家商品。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>超模 Jamie Bechert 为 3.1 Phillip Lim 的 2016 秋季新品拍摄了一组新的宣传片。这组宣传片取景于布鲁克林街头，Jamie Bechert 演绎了  3.1 Phillip Lim 的天鹅绒套装、长外套和高腰裤。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608120938561NXxVRgwatWQYZJv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812093850krPqs2nRGMpHL9lg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.723750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812093844Wv0yjLlhNOrTUzfx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.726250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812093833fYUlJjTFwN1HZ2eA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Kendall Jenner 登上了 VOGUE 九月刊的封面。这也是她首次登上 VOGUE 的封面。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608120939132Ps4w9RlgD6Fzkby.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.241164\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812093923hmPoGcz0yXpqNWMu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608120939341k4gC0lQtz9756xc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>LINE Friends 推出了日本限定版便当盒。定价为 2268 日元，仅在日本地区进行售卖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812093944tSfoC7e4BRpg2vjA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608120939538GPKLeODrENfjblV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812094001xYhbGBgHXqLr6iPR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">纽约知名摄影师 Thuan Tran 为人气工装品牌 Carhartt WIP 在东京街头拍摄了秋冬系列特辑。这组主题为「TALE OF TOKYO WANDERERS」的 lookbook 中，两位日本男性青年展示了「Carahrtt Athletic」、「Cart Racing」、「Military」 3 代主题系列。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608120940337QFAtjfTPeHN1XdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812094048ROaZ2uAQEBUW06pC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812094057Wp7aM6Q8lFtdBNIy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812094108I1Am3l8n9zc7NZJY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812094116FmcwV6x4JMhO0Sqf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686040\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812094124wistT2SjJuhV6Qz4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">美国休闲服饰品牌 Madewell 在 instagram 上发起了一个 “牛仔 everyday” 的活动，目前更新了一些图，还挺好看的。<a href=\"madewell.com/denimeveryday\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里</a>，查看更多。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608121056202PD35wslFZKNWzG9.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.003356\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608121056142O7iQP96xljKMDtJ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001681\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812094135RgsnJ4pliIEaWSKQ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.003361\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}